dialogue_1: Captain! Something strange is happening, my systems are showing an unidentified entity is trying to take over, it is speaking in a dialect I cannot understand!
dialogue_2: It is breaking through my firewalls Captain, communicating in 3 simple shapes, maybe they mean something! Quick the virus is taking over!
loss_dialogue: Oh no Captain! It broke through another wall!
Help, another firewall has been corrupted!
It is breaking through my AT-field!
win_dialogue: Yes Captain! We can do this!
Ha Ha! Take that, the encryption is working Captain
end_dialogue: We did it Captain! We managed to show that Unknown Entity who is boss! Shall we go for cake?
